{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HeGHU8mDMjBWRHw8nuZxyv","type":"tool_result","content":"280:- **`test-provable`** → Use **test-provable verification** (below). No Docker, no running the app.\n281:- **`runtime-provable`** → Use **runtime-provable verification** (below). Build and run the app locally — no Docker stack.\n282:- **`environment-provable`** → Use **environment-provable verification** (below). Full Docker flow.\n283:- **`escalate`** → Use **escalate verification** (below). Mixed-tier dispatch per AC.\n285:**test-provable verification (derived tier = test-provable):**\n333:**runtime-provable verification (derived tier = runtime-provable):**\n386:**escalate verification (derived tier = escalate):**\n402:**environment-provable verification (derived tier = environment-provable):** Full Docker container with no source code access."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01KTsf5fpoa7X5mTtM1qbqAV","session_id":"52ba63bf-4b91-451c-9abd-97fbda8291b9","uuid":"26d45a89-b818-40dd-9623-cc0c252e6d1b","timestamp":"2026-03-28T10:55:22.593Z"}
